high_descs: Turn right to face the bathtub.
Pick up the bar of soap from the bathtub.
Turn right and walk to the wall, then turn left and go to the sink.
Put the soap in the sink, wash it off, then pick it back up.
Turn around and turn right, walk past the bathtub to the trash can on the floor. Turn left to face the toilet.
Put the bar of soap on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean bar of soap on top of the toilet.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the tub.
Look to the floor and grab the soap.
Turn right and then left to go to the sink.
Put the soap into the sink and turn the water on.
Grab the soap and go to the toilet.
Put the soap down on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Grab the soap from the tub put it in the sink. Put it on the floor by the toilet.

high_descs: Turn right and face the rear of the bath tub.
Take the pink soap bar from the bath tub.
Go to the sink to the right of the tub.
Place the soap in the sink. Turn the water on and off. Take the soap from the sink.
Turn left and go to the right side of the toilet, then face the toilet.
Put the soap on top of the toilet next to the pink soap.
anns.task_desc: Put clean soap on top of a toilet.
